archived_events.description: Fresh local produce, baked goods, and handcrafted items. Get the best selection by arriving early!

archived_events.description: Join us for our weekly community garden meetup. We'll be planting winter vegetables and discussing plans for the spring season. All skill levels welcome!

archived_events.description: Monthly open mic night featuring local musicians, poets, and performers. Sign up starts at 7 PM, performances begin at 8 PM. Free entry, donations appreciated.

archived_events.description: This month we're discussing 'The Midnight Library' by Matt Haig. Coffee and snacks provided. New members always welcome!

archived_events.description: Start your day with a free outdoor yoga session suitable for all levels. Bring your own mat and water. Weather permitting.

archived_events.description: Join fellow runners for a refreshing morning run through the city. All paces welcome. Meet before sunrise!

archived_events.description: Relax with afternoon tea while discussing contemporary art. This week featuring local artist exhibitions.
